title: Cold Chisel - Last Stand (Soundtrack - CD) @320kbps
description:
Cold Chisel&#039;s &#039;Last Stand&#039; concert was recorded and filmed at the Sydney Entertainment Centre in December 1983.

Cold Chisel is one of the most successful bands in Australian rock history. Formed in 1973 in Adelaide, by 1979 they were the biggest live draw around Australia. Their popularity was vividly demonstrated when, on breaking up in 1983, their &#039;Last Stand&#039; concerts played 26 shows, including five at the Sydney Entertainment Centre. Since then Cold Chisel have gone on to sell over 3 million albums and CDs.
